# Track: commands, config, templates
# Ignore: portfolio state, logs, performance data, watchlist analyses, archives

# Portfolio state
PORTFOLIO.md

# Watchlist ticker files and index (but track the template)
watchlist/*.md
!watchlist/_template.md

# Decision logs (but track templates)
log/decisions/*.md
!log/decisions/_template.md
!log/decisions/_prune_template.md

# Review logs (but track template)
log/reviews/*.md
!log/reviews/_template.md

# Risk logs (but track template)
log/risk/*.md
!log/risk/_template.md

# Performance data (but track template)
performance/RETURNS.md
performance/BENCHMARK.md
performance/SNAPSHOTS.md

# Archives — all state-specific
closed/*.md
passed/*.md
